<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Uyim-joyim mening panohim
 Sening qoĘ»lingda Ra
 Butun borliq mening orzuim
 Seni deb Rabbim kechdim

[P1]
   YigĘ»ladim quvondim seni borligingni bildim
   QoĘ»llarimni koĘ»tarib Iso seni dedim

[C1]
   // Endi qoĘ»lingda oilam
   Endi qoĘ»lingda ota-onam
   Endi qoĘ»lingda hayotim Rabbim
   Endi qoĘ»lingda aka-ukam //

[V2]
 Endi bildim hech narsa oĘ»zgarmas
 Ishonmasam men senga
 OĘ»z-oĘ»zimdan kechirim boĘ»lmasam
 Loyiq boĘ»lolmayman senga

[P2]
   Izladim soĘ»radim seni xoxishingni bildim
   Qancha sevsan meni
   Shuncha yaqin boĘ»ldim senga</lyrics>
<title>Endi QoĘ»lingda</title>
</song>